### Test 1: Create a Lecture
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lectures
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Neural Networks - Lecture 1",
  "sourceType": "audio",
  "audioPath": "lecture-audio/user-123/nn-1.mp3",
  "language": "en",
  "networkMode": "normal"
}

###

### Test 2: Transcribe Audio
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transcribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lectureId": "f2d2af4a-3769-477f-bf26-62195de45b1a",
  "audioPath": "lecture-audio/user-123/nn-1.mp3",
  "provider": "groq",
  "language": "en"
}

###

### Test 3: Transform Transcript (Mocked GitHub Models)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transform
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lectureId": "f2d2af4a-3769-477f-bf26-62195de45b1a",
  "transcript": "Today we cover perceptrons and gradient descent...",
  "targetLanguage": "en",
  "networkMode": "adaptive",
  "provider": "github-models"
}
